AppGrid User Control Class v1.72     (Last updated: 08-Dec-97)
==============================================================

The AppGrid user control can be painted on a form to provide 
the functionality of a an appointment booking grid. It is a 
subclass of the standard BaseControl class.


AppGrid Control Interface
==============================================================

--------------------------------------------------------------
Attributes					Type
--------------------------------------------------------------
allAppGridResources			AppGridResourceDict
appColor					Integer
appLabel					AppGridAppLabel
appLabels					AppGridAppLabelDict
appLabelsSelected			AppGridAppLabelDict
appResources				ObjectArray
appStatColor				Integer
appStatHeight				Integer
appStatWidth				Integer
backColor					Integer
changeType					Integer
columnWidth					Integer
endTime						Time
foreColor					Integer
firstColumnWidth			Integer
firstRowHeight				Integer
fontBold					Boolean
fontItalic					Boolean
fontName					String
fontSize					Integer
fontStrikethru				Boolean
fontUnderline				Boolean
gridColor					Integer
infoColor					Integer
multiSelect					Boolean
rowHeight					Integer
scrollDirection				Integer
startTime					Time
timeGrid					Integer
timeSnap					Integer
overlapping					Boolean
overlaying					Boolean

appLabel.appObject			Object
appLabel.appGrid			AppGrid
appLabel.auxObject			Object
appLabel.caption			String
appLabel.color				Integer
appLabel.duration			Integer
appLabel.extObject			Object
appLabel.moveable			Boolean
appLabel.resource			Object
appLabel.selected			AppGrid
appLabel.sizeable			Boolean
appLabel.start				Time
appLabel.status				AppGridStatusLabel

appLabel.status.bitmap		Picture
appLabel.status.caption		String
appLabel.status.color		Integer
appLabel.status.visible		Boolean

--------------------------------------------------------------
AppGridResource Class Attributes/References
--------------------------------------------------------------
caption						String (used for display method)
date						Date
extObject					Object
myAppGrid					AppGrid
string						String
time						Time

--------------------------------------------------------------
Methods
--------------------------------------------------------------
addAppLabel(objResource, timStartTime, intDuration)
addResource(objResource)
clearGrid()
deselectAll()
getColumn(relY)
getRow(relX)
getResource(relX)
getTime(relY)
getX(objResource)
getY(timTime)
isValidX(relX)
isValidY(relY)
paintGrid(objResource, timStartTime, intDuration, intBackColor, strText, intTextColor)
removeAllAppLabels()
removeAllResources()
removeResource(objResource)
scrollTo(appLabel)
select(appLabel, blnSelect)
setGridScale(intRowHeight, intColWidth, intFirstRowHeight, intFirstColWidth)
setGridTime(timStartTime, timEndTime, intTimeGrid)
setTitle(strTitle)

appLabel.remove()
appLabel.set(objResource, timStartTime, intDuration)

--------------------------------------------------------------
Events
--------------------------------------------------------------				
click
dblClick
dragDrop
dragOver
mouseDown
mouseMove
mouseUp
scrolled

--------------------------------------------------------------
changeType	Description		Events
--------------------------------------------------------------				
0			No change		Click, DblClick, MouseDown, MouseUp
1			Drop			DragDrop
2			Move			DragDrop
3			Resize			Click, MouseDown, MouseUp
4			Status Click	MouseDown, MouseUp


---------------------------------------------------------------
Constants					Type			Value
---------------------------------------------------------------
ChangeType_Drop				Integer			1
ChangeType_Move				Integer			2
ChangeType_NoChange			Integer			0
ChangeType_Resize			Integer			3
ChangeType_StatusClick		Integer			4</text>
